OL,3,CHuman remains identified as father
OL,4,Cmissing for 13 years
OL,6,FRemains found in woodland near
OL,7,FHuddersfield have been identified as
OL,8,Fthose of a father-of-three who went
OL,9,Fmissing 13 years ago.
OL,11,FKevin Judge, a former miner, was 68 at
OL,12,Fthe time of his disappearance from the
OL,13,FLupset area of Wakefield in April 2013.
OL,15,FHis remains were found in January in a
OL,16,Fwooded area off Kiln Lane between
OL,17,FClayton West and Emley, near
OL,18,FHuddersfield.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/6
