PN,36802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1773069077
OL,3,CHuman remains identified as father
OL,4,Cmissing for 13 years
OL,6,FHe was identified from dental records
OL,7,Fand a set of house keys found at the
OL,8,Fscene, his family said.
OL,10,FThe discovery of the remains initially
OL,11,Fprompted an investigation by the West
OL,12,FYorkshire Homicide and Major Enquiry
OL,13,FTeam (HMET).
OL,15,FBut the force has since said his death
OL,16,Fis not being treated as suspcious
OL,18,FMr Judge's daughter Louise Wilson told
OL,19,Fthe Yorkshire Live website she felt
OL,20,Fsome relief to finally find out what
OL,21,Fhappened to her father.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,369,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1773069077
OL,3,CHuman remains identified as father
OL,4,Cmissing for 13 years
OL,6,FShe described him as a "typical
OL,7,FYorkshire bloke" and a witty man who
OL,8,Fenjoyed visiting pubs in Wakefield
OL,9,Fcity centre and who was "a bit of a
OL,10,Fcharacter".
OL,12,FHe may have been suffering from the
OL,13,Fearly stages of dementia, Ms Wilson
OL,14,Fsaid.JShe said: "I thought he had been
OL,15,Fkilled. It was just strange him
OL,16,Fdisappearing.
OL,18,F"It's a mystery why he has gone that
OL,19,Fway. He loved walking, but why he went
OL,20,Fthere I don't know."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
