PN,36804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1773069077
OL,3,CHuman remains identified as father
OL,4,Cmissing for 13 years
OL,6,FShe her father's disappearance had
OL,7,Fcontinued to affect his ex-wife
OL,8,FSheila, saying: "Mum died three years
OL,9,Fago. She was always fretting about
OL,10,Fhim. She would mention him two or
OL,11,Fthree times a week and was always
OL,12,Flooking in the papers. She was always
OL,13,Fthinking about him."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
