PN,36805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1773069077
OL,3,CHuman remains identified as father
OL,4,Cmissing for 13 years
OL,6,FDet Supt Damian Roebuck, of the
OL,7,FHomicide and Major Investigation Team,
OL,8,Fsaid: "Following the discovery made in
OL,9,FJanuary we have worked with a number
OL,10,Fof experts to carry out tests, and we
OL,11,Fare now confident that these remains
OL,12,Fhave been identified and that there
OL,13,Fare no suspicious circumstances
OL,14,Fsurrounding the death.
OL,16,F"Kevin's family are being supporting
OL,17,Fby specialist officers and I hope this
OL,18,Fdevelopment may start to bring them
OL,19,Fsome closure following the long-
OL,20,Frunning investigation into his
OL,21,Fdisappearance."
OL,26,@pD@GOUxD@AOU
